		are better desktop files for "Add User" and "Configure
		Network"

2005-11-03  Scott Reeves  <sreeves@novell.com>
	* control-center/src/control-center.c
	  control-center/etc/Makefile.am
	  libslab/src/slab-gnome-util.h
